headline: Archer Daniels to cease operations at Bushnell plant
summary: ADM announced that it is taking actions to streamline its global soy protein production network at its recently recommissioned soy protein facility in Decatur, Illinois, as well as other facilities spanning its network. ADM plans to cease operations at its plant in Bushnell, Illinois. These changes are part of the company’s broader focus on optimizing and simplifying its portfolio.
